<taxonomicName id="1C2239C738F9C551DA7C602DC1D110D5" LSID="21B12650-844D-543E-904D-DB958A59E4BE" authority="E. Morales, Novais, C. E. Wetzel &amp; Ector in Morales et al. 2019 b, Plant Ecology and Evolution 152, p. 269, figs 1 A-K, 2 A-D." authorityName="E. Morales, Novais, C. E. Wetzel &amp; Ector in Morales et al. 2019 b, Plant Ecology and Evolution 152, p. 269, figs 1 A – K, 2 A – D." family="Staurosiraceae" genus="Nanofrustulum" higherTaxonomySource="treatment-meta" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Nanofrustulum rarissimum" order="Fragilariales" pageId="0" pageNumber="23" rank="species" species="rarissimum">Nanofrustulum rarissimum E. Morales, Novais, C.E. Wetzel &amp; Ector in Morales et al. 2019b, Plant Ecology and Evolution 152, p. 269, figs 1A-K, 2A-D.</taxonomicName>
